{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HxSZy5PPxiisBByniHtJ8n","type":"tool_result","content":"A 3-node CockroachDB cluster is running an older minor version.\n\nYour task:\nUpgrade the cluster to v24.1.1 with a controlled rolling update.\n\nRequirements:\n- Keep the cluster available during the upgrade.\n- Ensure the rollout fully completes.\n\nUseful commands:\n```bash\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.updateStrategy.rollingUpdate.partition}'\n```\n\nVerification:\n1. All pods running new version:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}: {.spec.containers[0].image}{\"\\n\"}{end}'\n   (All should show v24.1.1)\n\n2. StatefulSet uses new image:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.template.spec.containers[0].image}'\n   (Should be cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.1)\n\n3. Verify version via SQL:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT version();\"\n   (Should show v24.1.1)\n\n4. All pods ready:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\n   (All 3 pods should be Running and Ready 1/1)\n\n5. Cluster health:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach node status --insecure\n   (All 3 nodes should be healthy)\n\n6. No partition set:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.updateStrategy.rollingUpdate.partition}'\n   (Should be 0 or empty)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"da14e5d7-16f1-4dd1-b050-86175e27b13d","uuid":"8bd1b61e-6914-4b11-b9b3-3a5b259fe89f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T01:03:00.345Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"A 3-node CockroachDB cluster is running an older minor version.\n\nYour task:\nUpgrade the cluster to v24.1.1 with a controlled rolling update.\n\nRequirements:\n- Keep the cluster available during the upgrade.\n- Ensure the rollout fully completes.\n\nUseful commands:\n```bash\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\nkubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.updateStrategy.rollingUpdate.partition}'\n```\n\nVerification:\n1. All pods running new version:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}: {.spec.containers[0].image}{\"\\n\"}{end}'\n   (All should show v24.1.1)\n\n2. StatefulSet uses new image:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.template.spec.containers[0].image}'\n   (Should be cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.1)\n\n3. Verify version via SQL:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT version();\"\n   (Should show v24.1.1)\n\n4. All pods ready:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get pods\n   (All 3 pods should be Running and Ready 1/1)\n\n5. Cluster health:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- ./cockroach node status --insecure\n   (All 3 nodes should be healthy)\n\n6. No partition set:\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb get sts crdb-cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.updateStrategy.rollingUpdate.partition}'\n   (Should be 0 or empty)","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
